{"id":37518,"date":"2021-12-15T11:29:02","date_gmt":"2021-12-15T07:29:02","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=37518"},"modified":"2021-12-15T11:30:27","modified_gmt":"2021-12-15T07:30:27","slug":"tafseer-quran-by-quran","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/15\/tafseer-quran-by-quran\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Tafsir: The Prophet explains the Quran with Quran"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Umm Mubashir reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said in front of Hafsah, \u201c<strong>No one among my companions will enter the Hellfire, if Allah wills, those who pledged beneath the tree.<\/strong>\u201d She said, \u201cWhy not, O Messenger of Allah?\u201d The Prophet admonished her and Hafsah recited the verse, \u201c<strong>There are none of you but that he will come to it,<\/strong>\u201d (19:71). The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Allah Almighty said: Then, We will save those who were righteous and and leave the wrongdoers within it upon their knees<\/strong>.\u201d (19:72)<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2496<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong> (authentic) according to Muslim<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u0646 \u0623\u064f\u0645\u0651 \u0645\u064f\u0628\u064e\u0634\u0651\u0650\u0631\u064d \u0642\u0627\u0644\u062a \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0639\u0650\u0646\u0652\u062f\u064e \u062d\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0635\u064e\u0629\u064e <strong>\u0644\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u062f\u0652\u062e\u064f\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0631\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0634\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0645\u0650\u06